@startuml
title Viaverse Capability — State Diagram

[*] --> NOT_ENABLED
NOT_ENABLED --> PENDING_ONBOARDING : start onboarding
PENDING_ONBOARDING --> PENDING_REVIEW : submit verification if required
PENDING_REVIEW --> ENABLED : approved
PENDING_ONBOARDING --> ENABLED : no review required
ENABLED --> SUSPENDED : policy / risk / admin
SUSPENDED --> ENABLED : appeal / fix issue
SUSPENDED --> REVOKED : severe / final
REVOKED --> PENDING_ONBOARDING : re-apply if policy allows
ENABLED --> ACCOUNT_DELETED : account deletion
SUSPENDED --> ACCOUNT_DELETED : account deletion
ACCOUNT_DELETED --> [*]

note bottom
The same state machine applies per capability:
REQUEST_WORK, DO_WORK_INDIVIDUALLY, OPERATE_BUSINESS,
SOCIAL_PARTICIPATION, and admin capabilities.
end note
@enduml
